      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2025-10",
        "text": "Working with Zack was very easy from start to finish. He was very attentive and communicative throughout the whole process, despite ours was a very modest occasion with no frills in-between. We were worried that the venue setup was too dark and dull to have nice photos, but despite the challenges Zack managed to capture the sweetest, warmest memories of that night. Thank you Zack, for being part of our small celebration!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2023-06",
        "text": "Zak has been amazing to work with. He has an eye for detail and has the ability to encapsulate every emotion into print. Through his photos I could relive my wedding all over again, marvelling at faces I saw briefly at my wedding but now forever captured in print. He takes the time to know you personally before shooting the wedding so it feels like having a friend over, instead of just a photographer.\n\nWe loved his works so much, we asked him again to shoot our daughter’s naming ceremony. When you engage Zak, you get more than just a photographer!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2023-06",
        "text": "We’re really glad to have engaged Zakaria to capture the rawness of the emotions felt on our wedding. The portraits he took of us still remain my favourite photos till today and we display them in our house to remind us of our very special day. He also has this ability make everyone really comfortable and just be ourselves so the candid photos turned out really wonderful as well. Zack also has a really keen eye for detail and can compose very lovely photos with seemingly normal backdrops and turn them into very beautiful photos. We are so grateful for his kindness and professionalism. I would 10/10 recommend engaging him for capturing your special moments."
